lect up to 3 priorities. 3 AI Journey: AI maturity stage. 4 Data and Leadership: data readiness and leadership commitment. 5 Challenge: biggest challenge text area. 6 Email and OTP placeholder: email field and clearly-labelled OTP placeholder state. Do not send OTP. Do not call backend. Add optional budget and geography only if they fit cleanly. Design should feel like an expensive enterprise self-assessment tool with progress rail, animated transitions, summary preview, and mobile-friendly step layout. Use local state only. Enforce validation before moving to next step. Result generation can remain existing if already present; this task focuses on the input wizard quality. Run lint and build.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"44-phase3-blueprint-scoring-engine-and-results\",\n    \"title\": \"Finalize Blueprint scoring engine and results report\",\n    \"scope\": \"phase3-tool\",\n    \"target\": \"/build/blueprint scoring and results\",\n    \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n    \"prompt\": \"Finalize the Blueprint Generator scoring engine and results report. Do not touch landing page unless shared Blueprint logic requires a safe bug fix, and do not alter hero UI. Use exact formula: Blueprint Score = 0.20(AI Maturity) + 0.25(Business Need) + 0.20(Data Readiness) + 0.20(Process Complexity) + 0.15(Transformation Readiness). AI Maturity scores: No AI 10, Exploring AI 30, Running Pilots 60, Scaling AI 85, AI-Driven Enterprise or AI-Native 100. Business Need: Reduce Costs/Cost Reduction 20, Improve Productivity/Productivity 20, Improve Customer Experience/Customer Experience 15, Increase Revenue/Revenue Growth 15, Strengthen Compliance/Compliance 10, AI Transformation 20, Automate Processes 20, capped at 100. Data Readiness: Highly fragmented 20, Partially connected 50, Mostly integrated 75, Fully integrated 100. Process Complexity: <100 20, 100-1000 50, 1000-10000 80, 10000+ 100. Transformation Readiness: Not Discussed 20, Exploring 50, Budget Approved 80, Executive Mandate 100. Score categories: 0-25 AI Beginner, 26-50 AI Explorer, 51-70 AI Adopter, 71-85 AI Transformer, 86-100 AI-Native Leader. Test case Banking, 15000 employees or 10000+ company size, Scaling AI, Productivity + Cost Reduction + Compliance, Mostly Integrated Data, Budget Approved must show 87/100. Results must include AI Readiness Score, category, dimension breakdown, Top 5 Recommended AI Opportunities, Recommended GFF AI Solution, Expected Business Impact, and 90-Day Roadmap: Garage Discovery, Foundry Pilot, Factory Enterprise Rollout, Operate Managed AI Operations. Impact labels must be expected/modelled, not guaranteed. Create premium report UI with charts or visual score rings using CSS/SVG only, no fake dashboards. Run lint and build.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"45-phase3-blueprint-local-save-share-copy\",\n    \"title\": \"Add local save copy and share-ready Blueprint report actions\",\n    \"scope\": \"phase3-tool\",\n    \"target\": \"/build/blueprint report actions\",\n    \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n","success":true}],"durationMs":20}}
